text: Bučići is a village in the vicinity of Novi Travnik, Bosnia and Herzegovina. Its population was around 1,600 in 2007, 99% of whom were Croat, with the remainder belonging to unspecified ethnic groups. Most of the residents are Roman Catholic. == Notable people from Bučići == * Marijan Šunjić * Frano Zubić Category:Villages in the Federation of Bosnia and Herzegovina hr:Bučići
